ygData.messageBody:
able to find out what to do. See, I bought a
friend's EQ: Ruins of K. and I really don't know what to
do with it. <br>Since he was shipped out (military)
he didn't tell me much about it. Guess he took it
for granted that I'd know all about it. <br>Well, I
installed it and then found out I couldn't use it cause I
don't have his information to access the
account!<br>From what I figure he didn't use it much either. But
how do I go about getting connected and all
that?<br>I'm hoping to find out more about EQ here, so I won't
feel so blasted lost when I finally try it
out.<br>SO...any helpful suggestions?<br><br>Lady DM
